    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p><i>15th-level Swarmkeeper feature</i></p><p>You can discorporate into your swarm, avoiding danger. When you take damage, you can use your reaction to give yourself resistance to that damage. You vanish into your swarm and then teleport to an unoccupied space that you can see within 30 feet of you, where you reappear with the swarm.</p><p>You can use this feature a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus, and you regain all expended uses when you finish a long rest.</p></div>",
